--- OCIChangeLog	(revision 1355)
+++ OCIChangeLog	(revision 1356)
@@ -1,3 +1,16 @@
+Tue Oct 27 19:30:09 UTC 2009  Chris Cleeland  <cleeland@ociweb.com>
+
+          Imported the following change from OCITAO 1.4a.
+
+        * ace/Select_Reactor_Base.h:
+        * ace/Select_Reactor_Base.cpp (read_notify_pipe):
+
+          Changed the second recv() that is used in case of a short first
+          read to be a recv_n(), blocking until the rest of the buffer can
+          be received on the pipe.  The problem was discovered during
+          routine testing (Notify_Performance_Test) on VxWorks 6.7 on a P3
+          platform, but could occur on any platform.
+
 Sat Oct 24 06:14:18 UTC 2009  Steven Stallion  <stallions@ociweb.com>
 
         * OCIReleaseNotes.html:
